{"tid":264991,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想出格貨van公私兩用。邊格好？","createTime":"2017-05-31T09:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T10:23:26.000Z","uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21505a5c7add2726fc299dd2de1eb49412dcadb8","tid":264991,"uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"我目標想出無死期客貨van...我有份正職地盤返。有時會車下啲工具咁。無野車果時就唸住當私家車咁用。仲有閒時唸住跑下台幫補下當係兼職咁<br />\n有三款係考慮當中<br />\nHiace 好在係維修好似易啲同多件同二手價硬。但係就最貴同無咁好座<br />\nH1就三款之中最平 座都舒服 但係維修問題就唔知情況點<br />\nBenz vito 座過最舒服又有電門。有私家車感覺<br />\n但聽聞維修好金<br />\n請問巴打有無意見俾到小弟我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問過啲朋友，好多都叫我出hiace算<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c1a0a097be7104f1836dbfcbdfd8671966d835","tid":264991,"uid":29423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"以為你用貨van開格仔鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格"},{"pid":"87ffae6ca4a8b146278a057403283f97b60035be","tid":264991,"uid":29423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你用貨van開格仔鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格格</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soundcloud.com/jack-sze/ikea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soundcloud.com%2Fjack-sze%2Fikea&d=jl7n1qwn2WWIzNfmHyC6m4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5279a4f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soundcloud.com/jack-sze/ikea</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba083bcb01c52dae6fec3701dd502c9d749b0f3","tid":264991,"uid":1715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"H1平買貴整 hiace零件貴極有限又多2手件 唔洗煩 如果要裝長梯既話hiace啦 其他車會唔夠長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c6cc1b2a64b7a6e695e3cad2f8c00b54062961","tid":26499