 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nT5果時  都係得前置打埋尾籠<br />\nt6有拿?!   但係樓豬想要架冇年期嘅車.......<br />\n<br />\nhi屎  通街都有得整。。低價位<br />\n<br />\nt5壞親都係關電腦野事     下下都要返廠<br />\n返廠郁d都2日起跳。。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同意hiace通街都有得整<br />\n副廠零件多<br />\n維修方便同埋會平d<br />\n呢個的確係優勢<br />\n<br />\n其實方間都已經有唔少街鋪專做福士van<br />\n如果講返廠整計hiace都唔會話快d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己試完車就真係覺得福士爽d<br />\n車空間大<br />\n駕駛感覺好d<br />\n又唔洗乾煎雙蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都肥<br />\nhiace 真係好夾好窄<br />\n唔係咁舒服<br />\n同埋講省油真係hiace 輸唔少<br />\n<br />\n不過嬲豬要買無死期<br />\n可以唔洗睇我上面堆廢話<br />\nbtw其實無死期只係將來政府有機會係部車退役時有錢退<br />\n唔係等於永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上年出車時都有諗呢d問題<br />\n最後出新車好過<br />\n真係用到15年都係返到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4b80bcc0987a470400d1b272e9128330dd07fe","tid":264991,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tnu23kf5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftnu23kf5&h=22d00ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗緊 VW caddy，有冇同好？"},{"pid":"167925c678e8437e27d6de3df78fe47a0f97262c","tid":264991,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為格仔vans鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係"},{"pid":"0dd3eac5e0ce2cbb14cf352f2f5f2309772c47c0","tid":264991,"uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"不過如果出新車就緊係唔屌hiace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有更多更平更好選擇"},{"pid":"d7667ef280b0be33425fbaa8de6daa482c8365d3","tid":264991,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過如果出新車就緊係唔屌hiace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有更多更平更好選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你真係要買無死期既<br />\n好多HIACE都好殘<br />\n可能撚起手都20萬公里 3~4年車咁<br />\n但因為冇死期同豐田在前<br />\n二手個價都唔會平過你出部新得15年命既其他牌子<br />\n嬲豬自己諗下啦<br />\n架車就你自己渣既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb99dbdf3c7102f0805e690cee92417f9feaf228","tid":264991,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dgo4h71z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdgo4h71z&h=9c680fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nExpert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9448bf7300e88d66dff7827ba50351a516d82e88","tid":264991,"uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過如果出新車就緊係唔屌hiace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有更多更平更好選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你真係要買無死期既<br />\n好多HIACE都好殘<br />\n可能撚起手都20萬公里 3~4年車咁<br />\n但因為冇死期同豐田在前<br />\n二手個價都唔會平過你出部新得15年命既其他牌子<br />\n嬲豬自己諗下啦<br />\n架車就你自己渣既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想買無死期就係預第日真係劏車都有退稅。至小有返個價係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過買二手車真係撞手神<br />\n我預算出部客貨車五千內月供到"},{"pid":"29a7ec59db50b378f41ecaad644de9da12c948a5","tid":264991,"uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/dgo4h71z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdgo4h71z&h=9c680fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nExpert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又轉左款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過聽講維修好食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e515b864c1ababcfa3e97c60f5072e482351eedf","tid":264991,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"Benz"},{"pid":"90f44c5c392380150d198a1941b040cc1e9f094d","tid":264991,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"Suzuki k van"},{"pid":"7c06aa2b6f7b38734974e3fdb0eb5dfec7058e21","tid":264991,"uid":15404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"買架舊alphard啦<br />\n<br />\n又放到工具，又見得人"}]}